N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 601.16 - Consultation with apprenticeship council

State Regulations

All determinations relating to the construction of Part 600
of this Title, and any revisions or changes to this Part and Part 600 of this

Title, shall be made by the commissioner after consultation with the
apprenticeship council. Notes
